data.description: ***UPGRADED EVERYTHING*** Like to entertain? Savor cooking in your chef's delight kitchen loaded with Granite counter-tops and kitchen island with travertine backsplash, custom oversized cabinets, 42'' GE Monogram built in fridge with custom panels, & stainless steel appliances including gas cooktop. Enjoy sunny days & mountain views in your lush tropical oasis backyard with sparkling pool & raised bed rose garden while cooking on your custom outdoor kitchen that includes 2 monogram fridges, granite counters, Thermador 36'' gas grill with sink and speakers! Gorgeous enormous open master bedroom suite with raised vanity granite countertops, dual sinks, large tub & separate shower, huge walk-in closet.  Enjoy cocktails and coffee from your custom wet-bar that includes a Sub-Zero built-in wine unit with 2 refrigerator doors, Scotsman clear ice cube maker, Thermador built-in coffee maker/espresso machine, & blak onyx bar top and backsplash. Separate large guest suite with private bathroom & granite countertops. Custom hardwood flooring throughout home. Vaulted ceilings, custom lighting, custom window treatments, custom hardwood flooring & faux paint throughout home. Formal Dining Room. Huge laundry room and cabinets with extra oven and utility sink. 3 car garage with cabinets. Custom front stonework, pavers entryway & front patio. Slate tile on the covered backyard patio. Auto-powered sun shade awnings out back help in the summertime. Sun screens. Alarm. Fenced dog kennel. Paver walkway with custom gate. NICEST HOME ON THE BLOCK!
